Enum Ternary

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Enum<Ternary>
org.revapi.Ternary
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Comparable<Ternary>
public enum Ternary extends Enum<Ternary>
Ternary logic using the Kleene algebra. The UNDECIDED value means just that - it doesn't mean "both true and false".
